description: The investment seeks to track the investment results of the FTSE EPRA/NAREIT Developed Europe Index composed of real estate equities in developed European markets. The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the underlying index. The underlying index measures the performance of companies engaged in the ownership and development of developed European real estate markets as defined by FTSE EPRA/NAREIT. The fund is non-diversified.
name: iShares Europe Developed Real Estate ETF
